latestIgtvVideos.title: The Lindt & Sprüngli Farming Program
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
What are the core pillars of the Lindt & Sprüngli Farming Program? 
The Lindt & Sprüngli Farming Program is based on 4 key pillars: (1) Traceability and Farmer Organization, (2) Training and Knowledge Transfer, (3) Farmer Investment and Community Development, (4) Verification and Continuous Process. Learn more about the Farming Program pillars in our video.  #Lindt  #Sustainability #Forabettertomorrow #FarmingProgram #Commitment

latestIgtvVideos.title: Lindt Home of Chocolate THE GRAND OPENING with Roger Federer
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Whoops! Guess who came one day too early? Roger Federer explores Switzerland's largest chocolate museum with the Lindt Maître Chocolatier. The Lindt Home of Chocolate is a magical experience for every chocolate lover. It houses an interactive chocolate world that will delight young and old alike. With a more than nine meter high chocolate fountain, a multimedia museum, a café, chocolate courses and the biggest Lindt chocolate shop in the world, the Lindt Home of Chocolate is an exciting chocolate experience for the whole family.

A tropical escape in every bite! 🌴🍫 Our Tropical Chocolate Fondue blends the smoothness of Excellence 55% Cocoa Milk Chocolate with the richness of Excellence 70% Cocoa Dark Chocolate, creating the ultimate dipping experience. Velvety, indulgent, and perfect for summer gatherings! 🍓🥭⁣
⁣
✨ Ingredients:⁣
⁣
 🔸 200g Lindt Excellence 70% Cocoa Dark Chocolate⁣
⁣
 🔸 175g Lindt Excellence 55% Cocoa Milk Chocolate⁣
⁣
 🔸 300ml double cream⁣
⁣
 🔸 30g butter⁣
⁣
So simple to make, yet absolutely divine! ⁣
